   Special Taxes Department

          The Special Taxes Department administers the fuel, excise, and
      environmental fee and tax programs. Information on many of the tax and
      fee programs administered by the Special Taxes Department is contained
                                in the links below.

                 Environmental Fees Division - General Information
                               Hazardous Substances Tax
                                      Activity Fee
                                      Disposal Fee
                                    Environmental Fee
                                      Facility Fee
                                      Generator Fee
